+-------------+
| WHAT I USE? |
+-------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                                                                                            |
| OS:               https://www.archlinux.org/                                               |
| Window manager:   https://hyprland.org/                                                    |
| Statusbar:        https://github.com/scorpion-26/gBar                                      |
| Terminal:         https://codeberg.org/dnkl/foot                                           |
| Launcher:         https://codeberg.org/dnkl/fuzzel                                         |
| Shell:            http://zsh.sourceforge.net/                                              |
| Editor:           https://neovim.io/                                                       |
| Video player:     https://mpv.io/                                                          |
| Music player:     https://cmus.github.io/                                                  |
| TUI File manager: https://github.com/gokcehan/lf                                           |
| GUI File manager: https://github.com/lxqt/pcmanfm-qt                                       |
| Web browser       https://librewolf-community.gitlab.io/                                   |
| PDF viewer:       https://pwmt.org/projects/zathura/                                       |
| Image viewer:     https://github.com/karlch/vimiv                                          |
| Fonts:            https://git.sr.ht/~ttr3dp/dots/blob/master/.config/fontconfig/fonts.conf |
| Notifications:    https://github.com/dunst-project/dunst                                   |
| Torrent client:   https://github.com/tremc/tremc                                           |
|                                                                                            |
